Resource Profile: openIMIS Contract

Official URL: https://github.com/openimis/openimis_fhir_r5_ig/StructureDefinition/openimis-contract Version: 0.1.0
Draft as of 2025-08-26 Computable Name: OpenIMISContract

Defines a Contract for openIMIS use to enrol a Family/Group. Mapped mostly to Policy and will link Group/Family and Patient/Insurees.

Usages:

  • Examples for this Profile: Contract/InformalSectorContract
  • CapabilityStatements using this Profile: openIMIS Capability Statement

You can also check for usages in the FHIR IG Statistics
